marketing: AeroShell Oil W100 Plus is a single grade oil that combines the single grade, ashless dispersant performance found in AeroShell Oil W100 and the anti-wear/anti-corrosion additives of AeroShell Oil W 15W-50 Multigrade. It is the oil for pilots who prefer a single grade but who also want the extra protection and performance.
